videos.headline: Michigan opens game with 50-yard kickoff return
videos.description: Michigan's Giles Jackson returns the opening kickoff 50 yards to set up Michigan with great field position for its opening drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan opens game with 50-yard kickoff return) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Michigan answers with Patterson TD pass
videos.description: Shea Patterson finds Nick Eubanks for a seven-yard touchdown to tie the game at 7-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan answers with Patterson TD pass) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Patterson passes Harbaugh on Michigan all-time passing list
videos.description: Shea Patterson finds Donovan Peoples-Jones for a 34-yard completion to pass Jim Harbaugh on Michigan's all-time passing list.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Patterson passes Harbaugh on Michigan all-time passing list) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Harris cartwheels into the end zone for Alabama TD
videos.description: Najee Harris bounces off a defender and flips into the end zone for the 9-yard touchdown to give Alabama the lead over Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harris cartwheels into the end zone for Alabama TD) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Michigan drills 57-yard field goal to take halftime lead
videos.description: Quinn Nordin's 57-yard field goal is good to give Michigan a 16-14 lead at halftime over Alabama.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan drills 57-yard field goal to take halftime lead) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Jones delivers a deep bomb to Smith for an Alabama TD
videos.description: Mac Jones drops back and finds DeVonta Smith on the 42-yard completion for an Alabama touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jones delivers a deep bomb to Smith for an Alabama TD) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Saban loses his cool on sideline, breaks headset
videos.description: Nick Saban is not pleased on the sideline and takes his anger out on his headset.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Saban loses his cool on sideline, breaks headset) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Jeudy's huge play sets up an Alabama TD
videos.description: Mac Jones finds Jerry Jeudy over the middle and Jeudy runs wild through the Michigan secondary for a 58-yard gain, setting up Jones' 20-yard touchdown pass to Miller Forristall on the next play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jeudy's huge play sets up an Alabama TD) 2020/01/01

videos.headline: Saban unsure if Tua will be medically ready for draft
videos.description: Nick Saban says he isn't qualified to answer if Tua Tagovailoa will be medically ready for the draft because he isn't a doctor and jokes that he's struggling to be a good coach.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Saban unsure if Tua will be medically ready for draft) 2020/01/01
